data.description: Welcome to your dream brick facade home nestled on a spacious half-acre lot! This meticulously maintained residence boasts elegance and functionality at every turn. The expansive living spaces are adorned with tasteful touches, including granite countertops, a tile backsplash, and a convenient breakfast bar—perfect for both casual meals and entertaining guests. Venture outdoors, and discover your own private oasis. A sprawling deck offers ample room for al fresco dining, lounging under the sun, or hosting unforgettable gatherings with loved ones. With plenty of space to roam and play, the lush backyard is a true haven for relaxation and recreation. Upstairs, the indulgent master suite awaits, complete with a trey ceiling adding architectural interest. Retreat to your sanctuary and unwind in the large ensuite bath, featuring double vanities and a soothing soaking tub—an ideal spot to melt away the stresses of the day. Convenience meets practicality with a large two-car garage and an extended driveway providing ample parking space. Whether you're a car enthusiast or simply seeking extra storage, this property has you covered. Don't miss the opportunity to make this impeccable home yours. Experience the epitome of comfort, style, and outdoor living—schedule your viewing today!
